Package grammar

Interface PickleCannonListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
Checker, PickleCannonBaseListener
public interface PickleCannonListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by PickleCannonParser.
